## 9. Upgrades

```bash
cd /opt/{{project_slug}}
git fetch --tags
git checkout v0.2.0          # the new release tag
make build-prod
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d
```

`up -d` recreates only the containers whose image changed. Named volumes are untouched.

If a release introduces a content/data migration, the release notes will say so explicitly and ship a migration script under `scripts/`.

